-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744454822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f6754dc6ad288d147da246%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreakup-lessons-ended-10-year-relationship-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Just%20before%20my%2031st%20birthday%2C%20I%20broke%20up%20with%20my%20partner%20of%2010%20years.%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20breakup%2C%20I%20became%20so%20much%20more%20confident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Maja%20Krasnicka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreakup-lessons-ended-10-year-relationship-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Probe%20Agency%20Takes%20Action%20On%20Key%20Properties%20In%20Congress-Linked%20Herald%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EProbe%20Agency%20Takes%20Action%20On%20Key%20Properties%20In%20Congress-Linked%20Herald%20Case%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20Saturday%20said%20it%20has%20issued%20notices%20to%20take%20possession%20of%20immovable%20assets%20worth%20Rs%20661%20crore%20that%20it%20had%20attached%20in%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%20against%20Congress-controlled%20Associated%20Journals%20Limited%20(AJL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notices%2C%20which%20seek%20vacation%20of%20the%20premises%2C%20were%20affixed%20at%20the%20Herald%20House%20at%20ITO%20in%20Delhi%2C%20at%20the%20premises%20in%20Bandra%20area%20of%20Mumbai%20and%20the%20AJL%20building%20located%20at%20Bisheshwar%20Nath%20Road%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20central%20agency%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20under%20Section%20(8)%20and%20Rule%205(1)%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%2C%20the%20central%20agency%20which%20investigates%20financial%20crimes%2C%20attached%20these%20immovable%20assets%20in%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20properties%20were%20attached%20after%20extensive%20investigation%20by%20ED%20which%20revealed%20signification%20generation%2C%20possession%20and%20use%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%20988%20crore.%20Therefore%2C%20to%20secure%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20and%20to%20prevent%20the%20accused%20from%20dissipating%20the%20same%2C%20the%20immovable%20properties%20of%20AJL%20located%20at%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%20and%20Lucknow%20valued%20at%20Rs.%20661%20crore%20along-with%20the%20shares%20of%20AJL%20valued%20at%2090.2%20crores%20were%20attached%20by%20issuing%20provisional%20attachment%20order%20(PAO)%20dated%2020.11.2023%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20and%20the%20same%20has%20been%20confirmed%20by%20the%20Ld.%20Adjudicating%20Authority%20on%2010.04.2024%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20by%20the%20ED%20into%20the%20case%20began%20in%202021%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20an%20order%20issued%20on%20June%2026%2C%202014%2C%20by%20the%20Metropolitan%20Magistrate%20Patiala%20House%20Courts%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20case%20is%20based%20on%20a%20private%20complaint%20filed%20by%20BJP's%20Subramanian%20Swamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20alleged%20a%20criminal%20conspiracy%20by%20several%20prominent%20political%20figures%2C%20including%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20a%20host%20of%20other%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20a%20private%20company%20Young%20Indian%20for%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20scheme%20related%20to%20the%20fraudulent%20takeover%20of%20properties%20valued%20over%20Rs%202000%20crore%20belonging%20to%20Associated%20Journals%20Limited%20(AJL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Herald%20is%20published%20by%20AJL%20and%20owned%20by%20Young%20Indian%20Private%20Limited.%20Congress%20leaders%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20are%20majority%20shareholders%20of%20Young%20Indian%20with%2038%20per%20cent%20shares%20held%20by%20each%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744454640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fbc0gotqg_herald-house-delhi_625x300_12_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprobe-agency-begins-process-of-taking-possession-of-herald-house-other-properties-in-national-herald-case-linked-to-congress-8147614%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Probe%20agency%20begins%20process%20of%20taking%20possession%20of%20Herald%20House%2C%20other%20properties%20in%20National%20Herald%20case%20linked%20to%20Congress%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20special%20operators%20are%20going%20all%20in%20on%20drones%20so%20that%20a%20human%20never%20has%20to%20make%20'first%20contact'%20with%20the%20enemy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225881%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20robot%20dog%20drone%20walks%20on%20brown%20grass%20in%20front%20of%20a%20group%20of%20people%20with%20green%20trees%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f9218a3fe8d3928362d0ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223921%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpecial%20forces%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20working%20with%20drones.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Sgt.%20Benjamin%20D.%20Castro%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUS%20special%20operations%20forces%20are%20working%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOperators%20said%20the%20speed%20of%20technological%20innovation%20requires%20constant%20learning.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEach%20type%20of%20uncrewed%20system%20has%20a%20different%20purpose%2C%20but%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20acquire%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20for%20cheap.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFORT%20BRAGG%2C%20