ng%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20playing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fwomens-basketball%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebasketball%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20I%20was%20five%20years%20old.%20I'm%20from%20New%20York%20City%2C%20and%20one%20of%20my%20earliest%20memories%20of%20the%20sport%20was%20traveling%20to%20Ocean%20City%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20to%20play%20in%20a%20tournament.%20I%20was%20the%20only%20girl%20on%20the%20team.%20But%20it%20didn't%20matter.%20Basketball%20soon%20became%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20played%20on%20the%20girls'%20team%20in%20high%20school.%20Then%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Boston%20College%2C%20where%20I%20joined%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fwomens-sports%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen's%20club%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20managed%20the%20varsity%20team%20while%20studying%20finance%20and%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20picking%20out%20basketball%20shoes%20for%20my%20senior%20year%2C%20I%20came%20across%20an%20ad%20featuring%20WNBA%20players.%20The%20ad%20pictured%20stars%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-sue-bird-doc-heading-to-netflix-brand-films-coup-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESue%20Bird%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20Diana%20Taurasi%20promoting%20other%20athletes'%20signature%20sneakers.%20Sue%20Bird%20held%20the%20Kyrie%204%20shoe%2C%20and%20Diana%20Taurasi%20held%20the%20LeBron%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20that%20ad%2C%20and%20it%20hit%20me.%20What%20is%20this%20saying%3F%20You%20can%20be%20the%20absolute%20best%20in%20the%20game%20but%20you%20will%20still%20be%20wearing%20and%20promoting%20sneakers%20named%20after%20someone%20else%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20into%20the%20issue%20and%20saw%20that%20not%20only%20is%20there%20a%20social%20implication%2C%20but%20a%20performance%20one%20as%20well.%20The%20female%20foot%20form%20differs%20in%20five%20key%20areas%2C%20including%20the%20ankle.%20So%2C%20when%20we%20play%20in%20these%20shoes%2C%20we're%20more%20at%20risk%20for%20knee%2C%20ankle%2C%20and%20leg%20injuries%20that%20are%20so%20common%20in%20basketball.%20It%20felt%20like%20a%20one-two%20punch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20as%20a%20senior%20in%20college%2C%20I%20started%20Moolah%20Kicks%20to%20create%20sneakers%20for%20female%20basketball%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%20name%20is%20slang%20for%20money%20and%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20street%20culture%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fncaa-college-womens-basketball-tv-ratings-popularity-wnba-caitlin-clark-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen's%20basketball%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20grew%20up%20with.%20It%20also%20signifies%20the%20financial%20opportunity%20the%20Moolah%20brand%20creates%20for%20female%20players%20with%20the%20help%20of%20our%20partners%20and%20the%20women's%20basketball%20community%20that%20has%20embraced%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bb8e927e-b751-4dee-8fd0-10559aec0424%5C%22%3EWorking%20with%20female%20athletes%20to%20grow%20the%20brand%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20work%20with%20female%20athletes%20to%20grow%20our%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWNBA%20player%20Courtney%20Williams%20wears%20our%20shoes.%20We've%20collaborated%20with%20major%20brands%2C%20including%20Stanley%2C%20and%20we've%20been%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BToday%26quot%3B%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20also%20expanded%20our%20reach%20into%20youth%20and%20amateur%20sports%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20Since%20we%20started%2C%20we%20have%20signed%20over%20100%20name%2C%20image%2C%20and%20likeness%20deals%20with%20athletes%20and%20gotten%20hundreds%20of%20Amateur%20Athletic%20Union%20teams%20to%20wear%20our%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20produce%20a%20shoe%20called%20the%20Press%20Break%20designed%20for%20girls'%20feet.%20We%20wanted%20girls%20to%20have%20shoes%20earlier%2C%20as%20young%20as%20in