hat%20every%20challenge%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20get%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoolah%20is%20a%20story%20about%20what%20happens%20when%20you%20lean%20into%20your%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20want%20to%20be%20synonymous%20with%20women's%20basketball.%20We%20want%20to%20create%20our%20own%20lane%20in%20which%20success%20is%20not%20compared%20to%20men's%20basketball.%20It's%20our%20own%20sport%2C%20our%20own%20identity%2C%20our%20own%20image%20and%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-built-women-basketball-sneaker-brand-college-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744450321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f5335fc6ad288d147d855f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-built-women-basketball-sneaker-brand-college-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Natalie%20White%20saw%20a%20problem%20in%20the%20basketball%20world%20and%20created%20her%20own%20shoe%20to%20fix%20it.%20Her%20brand%2C%20Moolah%20Kicks%2C%20is%20in%20631%20stores.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mmeaney%40businessinsider.com%20(Mackenzie%20Meaney)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-built-women-basketball-sneaker-brand-college-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSurrendered%20Like%20A%20Bonded%20Slave%26quot%3B%3A%20MK%20Stalin%20Rips%20Into%20BJP-AIADMK%20Alliance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20today%20described%20the%20renewed%20friendship%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20AIADMK%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcorrupt%20alliance%20of%20defeat%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Stalin%20accused%20both%20parties%20of%20mortgaging%20the%20state's%20autonomy%20for%20the%20pursuit%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin's%20remarks%20come%20a%20day%20after%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20visited%20Chennai%20and%20formally%20announced%20the%20reconstitution%20of%20the%20BJP-AIADMK%20alliance%20for%20the%202026%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20elections.%20The%20renewed%20partnership%20comes%20nearly%20two%20years%20after%20the%20two%20parties%20severed%20ties%20in%20September%202023%2C%20reportedly%20over%20contentious%20remarks%20made%20by%20BJP's%20K%20Annamalai%20about%20former%20AIADMK%20leaders%2C%20including%20former%20chief%20minister%20J%20Jayalalithaa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AIADMK-BJP%20alliance%20is%20an%20alliance%20doomed%20to%20fail.%20It%20was%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20who%20handed%20repeated%20defeats%20to%20this%20coalition.%20Now%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20reconstituted%20the%20same%20failed%20alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStalin%20questioned%20the%20lack%20of%20ideological%20clarity%20of%20the%20BJP-AIADMK%20pact%2C%20asserting%20that%20Mr%20Shah%20had%20failed%20to%20articulate%20the%20foundational%20principles%20on%20which%20the%20alliance%20rests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAIADMK%20claims%20to%20oppose%20NEET%2C%20the%20imposition%20of%20Hindi%2C%20the%20three-language%20policy%2C%20and%20the%20Waqf%20Act.%20They%20also%20claim%20to%20demand%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20representation%20should%20not%20be%20reduced%20during%20constituency%20delimitation.%20Are%20all%20these%20part%20of%20the%20'common%20minimum%20programme'%3F%20The%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20did%20not%20speak%20about%20any%20of%20these.%20Nor%20did%20he%20allow%20the%20AIADMK%20leadership%20to%20speak.%20Instead%2C%20he%20used%20the%20press%20conference%20solely%20to%20criticize%20the%20DMK%2C%20the%20DMK%20government%2C%20and%20me%20personally%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin%20went%20further%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20is%20currently%20probing%20NEET%20malpractices%20in%20five%20states%2C%20with%20arrests%20made%20among%20students%20and%20parents.%20%26quot%3BUnder%20whose%20control%20is%20the%20CBI%3F%20Let%20him%20look%20into%20this%20and%20then%20answer%20whether%20opposition%20to%20NEET%20is%20a%20distraction%20or%20a%20genuine%20effort%20to%20protect%20medical%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELaw%20and%20Order%3A%20Manipur%20vs%20Tamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20Mr%20Shah's%20criticism%20of%20law%20and%20order%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20drew%20a%20contrast%20with%20violence-hit%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20utterly%20condemnable%20for%20a%20Home%20Minister%20to%20irresponsibly%20claim%20that%20law%20and%20order%20has%20deteriorated%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20This%20is%20not%20Manipur%20-%20this%20is%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20ruled%20over%20a%20state%20where%20more%20than%20250%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20past%2018%20months.%20The%20Home%20Minister%20who%20failed%20to%20restore%20peace%20there%20now%20seeks%20to%20disturb%20peace%20in%20a%20peaceful%20state%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorruption%20Allegations%20Reignited%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20perhaps%20the%20most%20searing%20part%20of%20his%20statement%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20targeted%20AIADMK's%20alleged%20history%20of%20corruption%2C%20particularly%20singling%20out%20Jayalalithaa.%20%26quot%3BFormer%20Chief%20Minister%20Jayalalithaa%20had%20to%20step%20down%20twice%20due%20to%20corruption%20charges%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20sentenced%20to%20four%20years%20imprisonment%20in%20the%20disproportionate%20assets%20case%20by%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Bengaluru%20after%20years%20of%20legal%20proceedings.%20If%20the%20BJP%20forms%20an%20alliance%20with%20her%20party%2C%20can%20it%20still%20speak%20credibly%20about%20corruption%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20alleged%20that%20AIADMK%20functionaries%20fled%20to%20the%20BJP%20after%20two%20central%20raids%20to%20avoid%20prosecution.%20Mr%20Stalin%20also%20accused%20AIADMK%20of%20surrendering%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20autonomy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20leadership%20has%20a%20calculated%20plan%20to%20eradicate%20Tamil%20through%20Hindi%20imposition%2C%20to%20block%20Tamil%20people's%20progress%20through%20various%20conspiracies%2C%20and%20to%20undermine%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20rights%20through%20constituency%20delimitation.%20The%20AIADMK%2C%20which%20has%20long%20surrendered%20itself%20like%20an%20old%20bonded%20slave%20camp%2C%20is%20being%20coerced%20by%20threats%20to%20implement%20these%20conspiracies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Alliance%20Announcement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20declared%20that%20the%202026%20Assembly%20polls%20would%20be%20fought%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswami%20(EPS)%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20election%20will%20be%20fought%20at%20the%20national%20level%20under%20Narendra%20Modi's%20leadership%20and%20AIADMK%20chief%20Edappadi%20Palaniswami%20at%20state%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%201998%20alliance%20where%20the%20AIADMK-BJP%20combine%20won%2030%20of%2039%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20would%20return%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state.%20Mr%20Shah%20downplayed%20suggestions%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20influenced%20AIADMK's%20internal%20matters%20or%20that%20K%20Annamalai's%20removal%20had%20been%20a%20precondition%20for%20the%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEPS%20described%20the%20alliance%20as%20%26quot%3Bfounded%20on%20a%20shared%20vision%20for%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20progress%20and%20prosperity.%26quot%3B%20He%20praised%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20%26quot%3Bunwavering%20support%26quot%3B%20and%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20renewed%20alliance%20would%20usher%20in%20development%20for%20Tamil%20Nadu.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744450320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F2ndje6j_mk-stalin-amit-shah-eps-_625x300_12_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmk-stalin-bjp-aiadmk-tamil-nadu-corrupt-alliance-of-defeat-mk-stalin-rips-into-bjp-aiadmk-tie-up-8147208%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20today%20described%20the%20renewed%20friendship%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20AIADMK%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcorrupt%20alliance%20of%20defeat%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Stalin%20accused%20both%20parties%20of%20mortgaging%20the%20state's%20autonomy%20for%20the%20pursuit%20of%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shoppers'%20answer%20to%20tariffs%3A%20Go%20to%20Costco%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shoppers%20waited%20outside%20Costco.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b4cfb07bb3f854015d2610%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20shoppers%20appeared%20to%20have%20gravitated%20toward%20Costco%20in%20the%20days%20before%20Donald%20Trump's%20latest%20tariffs%20were%20set%20to%20take%20effect.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EShoppers%20have%20a%20plan%20for%20avoiding%20tariffs%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-items-from-costco-executive-member-2025-3%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECostco%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EW