%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20packaging%2C%20this%20tea%20was%20inspired%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bsoothing%20tincture%20of%20lemon%20and%20ginger%26quot%3B%20that%20Meghan%20has%20been%20making%20%26quot%3Bfor%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20Greek%20mother%20who%20believes%20chamomile%20tea%20can%20cure%20just%20about%20any%20ailment%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20a%20cold%2C%20a%20tummy%20ache%2C%20or%20a%20bout%20of%20sadness.%20When%20I%20poured%20a%20hot%20cup%20of%20Meghan's%20lemon%20ginger%20tea%20and%20breathed%20in%20deeply%2C%20the%20smells%20brought%20me%20back%20to%20being%20a%20kid%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20lemon%20and%20ginger%2C%20the%20blend%20has%20lemongrass%2C%20lemon%20peel%2C%20licorice%20root%2C%20and%20spearmint%20(all%20organic%2C%20of%20course).%20It%20makes%20for%20a%20very%20soothing%20cup%20of%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMeghan%20said%20the%20peppermint%20tea%20is%20%26quot%3Beasily%20the%20favorite%20tea%20in%20our%20home.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225871%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22As%20ever%20tea%20poured%20in%20a%20cup.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f94378a466d2b74ab2f2f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223914%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrying%20Meghan's%20peppermint%20tea.%3Cp%3EYasara%20Gunawardena%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20compared%20Meghan's%20peppermint%20tea%20to%20a%20bag%20from%20the%20Traditional%20Medicinals%20box%20I%20had%20in%20my%20kitchen%2C%20and%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20discern%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20two%2C%20although%20the%20As%20Ever%20bag%20had%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20deeper%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20exactly%20groundbreaking%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20nice%20cup%20of%20tea!%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20all%20that%20tea%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20for%20some%20crepes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225739%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22As%20ever%20crepe%20mix.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f943c93fe8d3928362da26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223826%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20%2414%20crepe%20mix%20from%20Meghan's%20As%20Ever%20line.%3Cp%3EYasara%20Gunawardena%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20does%20a%20crepe%20feel%20more%20special%20than%20a%20pancake%3F%20I%20don't%20know%2C%20but%20it%20does%2C%26quot%3B%20Meghan%20says%20before%20making%20a%20version%20of%20these%20crepes%20on%20her%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%20newsletter%20and%20the%20As%20Ever%20website%2C%20the%20mix%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20crepes%20Meghan%20ate%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchez-janou-paris-restaurant-review-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParisian%20caf%C3%A9s%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20she%20was%20backpacking%20as%20a%20student.%20She%20promises%20the%20%2414%20mix%20is%20%26quot%3Beasy%20to%20prepare%20and%20endlessly%20adaptable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI'd%20never%20made%20crepes%20before%2C%20so%20I%20was%20intrigued%20to%20see%20if%20it%20was%20as%20easy%20as%20Meghan%20promised.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225871%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22As%20ever%20crepe%20mix%20being%20mixed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f943fea466d2b74ab2f323%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223914%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaking%20the%20crepe%20batter.%3Cp%3EYasara%20Gunawardena%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20crepe%20was%20a%20pale%20and%20soggy%20mess%20that%20went%20straight%20into%20the%20trash.%20This%20is%20through%20no%20fault%20of%20Meghan's%20instructions%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0I'm%20just%20not%20a%20very%20confident%20home%20chef.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20Meghan%20repeatedly%20says%20in%20her%20show%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20not%20in%20the%20pursuit%20of%20perfection%2C%20we're%20in%20the%20pursuit%20of%20joy%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20I%20tried%20again.%20And%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20third%20crepe%2C%20I%20was%20getting%20the%20hang%20of%20it%2C%20and%20by%20the%20fifth%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20total%20pro.%20%26quot%3BAm%20now%20domestic%20goddess%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20thought%20to%20myself.%20(Apparently%2C%20my%20internal%20voice%20is%20now%20Bridget%20Jones.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMeghan's%20crepes%20were%20my%20favorite%20product%20from%20the%20As%20Ever%20line.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225871%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22As%20ever%20crepe%20with%20nutella%20spread%20on%20top.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f9442e3fe8d3928362da42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223914%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrying%20the%20crepes%20with%20hazelnut%20spread.%3Cp%3EYasara%20Gunawardena%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20making%20homemade%20crepes%20seemed%20extremely%20daunting%2C%20it%20was%20validating%20to%20know%20that%20even%20I%20could%20quickly%20whip%20them%20up%20at%20home.%20And%20they%20were%20delicious!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crepes%20came%20out%20light%20and%20crispy%2C%20providing%20a%20bit%20of%20crunch%20with%20each%20bite.%20I%20followed%20Meghan's%20recommendation%20to%20try%20them%20with%20a%20chocolate%20hazelnut%20spread%2C%20a%20lovely%20little%20sweet%20treat%20my%20boyfriend%20couldn't%20get%20enough%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20tried%20the%20crepes%20with%20the%20famous%20raspberry%20spread%20that%20started%20it%20all.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225541%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22As%20ever%20raspberry%20jam.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f94458c6ad288d147df07f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223694%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeghan's%20%2414%20raspberry%20spread%20in%20keepsake%20packaging.%3Cp%3EYasara%20Gunawardena%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMeghan%20calls%20herself%20a%20%26quot%3Bpreserving%20nerd%26quot%3B%20and%20clearly%20loves%20to%20make%20homemade%20batches.%20The%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex%20told%20Fortune%20that%20she'd%20been%20sending%20her%20homemade%20products%20to%20Netflix%20CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%20every%20Christmas%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%2414%20As%20Ever%20raspberry%20spread%20is%20based%20on%20her%20recipe%20and%20comes%20in%20a%20special%20keepsake%20box.%20According%20to%20the%20website%2C%20a%20%249%20version%20sans%20box%20will%20be%20available%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20raspberry%20spread%20tastes%20surprisingly%20fresh%20and%20homemade.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225871%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22As%20ever%20raspberry%20spread.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f94480a466d2b74ab2f34c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223914%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrying%20a%20spoonful%20of%20the%20raspberry%20spread.%3Cp%3EYasara%20Gunawardena%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20complaints%20that%20Meghan's%20raspberry%20spread%20is%20%26quot%3Brunny.%26quot%3B%20But%20as%20she%20notes%20on%20the%20website%2C%20the%20spread%20has%20been%20crafted%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bfluid%20texture%20so%20it%20can%20be%20drizzled%2C%20spread%2C%20poured%2C%20and%20enjoyed%20for%20so%20much%20more%20than%20your%20morning%20toast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20personally%20liked%20the%20texture%20and%20that%20I%20could%20see%20dozens%20of%20seeds%20in%20every%20spoonful.%20It%20made%20the%20spread%20feel%20like%20something%20a%20friend%20had%20crafted%20in%20their%20kitchen.%20It's%20slightly%20sweet%2C%20with%20a%20refreshing%20zing%20from%20its%20lemon%20juice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20ended%20the%20day%20by%20making%20Meghan's%20shortbread%20cookies%2C%20which%20came%20with%20a%20package%20of%20her%20flower%20sprinkles.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226053%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22As%20ever%20shortbread%20cookie%20mix.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f9450fc6ad288d147df0b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224035%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaking%20the%20batter%20for%20Meghan's%20shortbread%20cookies%20with%20flower%20sprinkles.%3Cp%3EYasara%20Gunawardena%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ran%20into%20a%20few%20issues%20while%20making%20the%20shortbread%20cookie%20mix%2C%20which%20costs%20%2414.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20box%20says%20that%20your%20batter%20should%20become%20%26quot%3Blight%20and%20creamy%2C%26quot%3B%20which%E2%80%A6%20wasn't%20the%20case%20for%20me.%20My%20batter%20was%20powdery%20and%20dry%2C%20and%20I%20struggled%20to%20roll%20the%20dough%20onto%20my%20counter%20without%20it%20breaking%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20panic%20Googling%2C%20I%20added%20a%20few%20drops%20of%20cold%20water%20to%20help%20bind%20the%20dough.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20form%20the%20dough%20into%20a%20log%20and%20placed%20it%20in%20my%20fridge%20for%20an%20hour%20to%20chill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20the%20dough%20had%20properly%20chilled%2C%20the%20cookies%20were%20ready%20in%2011%20minutes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225871%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22As%20ever%20shortbread%20cookies%20going%20in%20the%20oven.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f944e5c6ad288d147df0a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223914%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaking%20the%20shortbread%20cookies%20out%20of%20the%20oven.%3Cp%3EYasara%20Gunawardena%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20taking%20the%20dough%20out%20of%20the%20oven%2C%20I%20could%20easily%20slice%20the%20cookies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20filled%20two%20baking%20sheets%20with%20about%2020%20cookies%20and%20still%20had%20over%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20dough%20left%20over%20to%20store%20in%20my%20freezer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20topped%20off%20the%20cookies%20with%20more%20flow