ll-you-need-to-know%2Farticleshow%2F120228065.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspain-tightens-tourism-rules-all-you-need-to-know%2Famp_articleshow%2F120228065.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspain-tightens-tourism-rules-all-you-need-to-know%2Famp_articleshow%2F120228065.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20Wants%20US%20To%20Stop%20Changing%20Clocks%20For%20More%20Daylight.%20What%20It%20Means%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20once%20again%20called%20for%20an%20end%20to%20the%20practice%20of%20changing%20clocks%20for%20Daylight%20Savings%20Time.%20He%20urged%20Congress%20to%20stop%20shifting%20time%20twice%20a%20year%20as%20it%20adds%20an%20unnecessary%20financial%20burden%20on%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Trump%2C%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20House%20and%20Senate%20should%20push%20hard%20for%20more%20Daylight%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20day.%20Very%20popular%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20no%20more%20changing%20of%20the%20clocks%2C%20a%20big%20inconvenience%20and%2C%20for%20our%20government%2C%20A%20VERY%20COSTLY%20EVENT!!!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F114319659315817918%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFor%20decades%2C%20people%20have%20been%20debating%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20implement%20daylight%20saving%20time.%20Several%20politicians%20and%20leaders%20have%20demanded%20that%20this%20biannual%20practice%20be%20discontinued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20December%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20criticised%20the%20biannual%20clock%20change%20on%20social%20media.%20Back%20then%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Republican%20Party%20will%20use%20its%20best%20efforts%20to%20eliminate%20Daylight%20Saving%20Time%2C%20which%20has%20a%20small%20but%20strong%20constituency%2C%20but%20shouldn't!%20Daylight%20Saving%20Time%20is%20inconvenient%2C%20and%20very%20costly%20to%20our%20Nation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F113647254141876924%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20a%20few%20months%20after%20strongly%20supporting%20permanent%20Daylight%20Savings%20Time%2C%20he%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bfifty-fifty%20issue.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20half%20of%20the%20people%20want%20to%20keep%20changing%20timings%20every%20autumn%20and%20fall%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20don't%20want%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20I%20can%20do%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20like%20it%20one%20way%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20like%20it%20the%20other%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESenator%20Ted%20Cruz%20said%20that%20people%20would%20agree%20on%20stopping%20changing%20clocks%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20but%20there's%20disagreement%20on%20which%20time%20we%20should%20keep%20permanently.%20He%20said%20some%20want%20to%20extend%20evening%20sunlight%20as%20it%20is%20useful%20for%20playing%20sports%20and%20outdoor%20fun%2C%20while%20others%20prefer%20standard%20time%20as%20it%20leads%20to%20better%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEven%20in%202022%2C%20the%20bill%20proposed%20by%20the%20US%20Senate%2C%20led%20by%20Democrats%20at%20that%20time%2C%20urged%20the%20elimination%20of%20the%20twice-yearly%20changing%20of%20clocks.%20Since%20the%20Republican-controlled%20House%20did%20not%20take%20up%20the%20bill%2C%20it%20never%20reached%20then-President%20J