r%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPolice%20have%20arrested%20over%20a%20dozen%20Russian%20nationals%2C%20including%20Rudnev%2C%20who%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20religious%20group%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPregnant%20Woman%20Sparks%20Arrest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20investigation%20began%20after%20the%20Russian%20woman%20arrived%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20the%20Patagonian%20city%20of%20Bariloche%20to%20give%20birth%20on%20March%2021.%20She%20was%20accompanied%20by%20two%20other%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20was%20not%20their%20maiden%20visit%20as%20the%20hospital%20staff%20saw%20them%20four%20days%20earlier%20when%20they%20struggled%20to%20share%20how%20they%20were%20connected%20to%20the%20pregnant%20lady%20as%20well%20as%20their%20residence%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20Argentina's%20prosecutor%20and%20police%20reports%2C%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20looked%20nervous%20and%20malnourished%2C%20while%20she%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20speak%20much%20by%20her%20two%20companions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%20doctors%20were%20alarmed%20by%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20woman%20and%20her%20companions'%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAfter%20the%20child%20was%20born%2C%20the%20two%20women%20asked%20the%20hospital%20authorities%20to%20document%20the%20newborn's%20last%20name%20as%20'Rudnev%2C'%20insisting%20that%20he%20was%20the%20father%20of%20the%20child%2C%20the%20prosecutor's%20report%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKonstantin%20Rudnev%20Arrested%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20week%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20Argentine%20police%20managed%20to%20locate%20Konstantin%20Rudnev%20and%20arrested%20him%20at%20the%20Bariloche%20airport%20on%20March%2028.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmeduza.io%2Fen%2Ffeature%2F2025%2F04%2F01%2Fastro-planetary-karate-loses-again%5C%22%3EMeduza%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20total%20of%2014%20people%20were%20arrested%20as%20they%20attempted%20to%20fly%20to%20Brazil.%20Out%20of%20these%2C%20eight%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20at%20the%20airport%20in%20Bariloche%2C%20while%20six%20others%20were%20arrested%20in%20Buenos%20Aires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20two%20women%2C%20who%20accompanied%20the%20mother%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20were%20arrested%20in%20a%20raid%20of%20their%20shared%20home%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EArgentina%20prosecutor%20Fernando%20Arrigo%20believes%20that%20the%20woman%20might%20have%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20Ashram%20Shambala.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20them%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20a%20crime%20yet%2C%20as%20criminal%20investigations%20start%20with%20an%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHis%20office%20is%20probing%2021%20Russian%20nationals%20in%20total.%20They%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20part%20of%20a%20criminal%20organisation%20that%2C%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20sex%20trafficking%20and%20slavery%2C%20recruited%20a%2022-year-old%20woman%20brought%20from%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2025%2F04%2F11%2Famericas%2Frudnev-argentina-russia-intl-latam%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERudnev%2C%20a%20mechanical%20engineering%20graduate%20turned%20religious%20leader%2C%20established%20the%20religious%20group%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20used%20to%20tell%20his%20followers%20that%20he%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Balien%20from%20Sirius%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20messiah%20sent%20to%20the%20planet%20to%20save%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAshram%20Shambala%2