on%20of%20diverse%20native%20species%20like%20%3Cem%3Edhau%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EAnogeissus%20pendula%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20%3Cem%3Edhak%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EButea%20monosperma%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20%3Cem%3Esalai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EBoswellia%20serrata%3C%2Fem%3E)%20to%20restore%20the%20ecological%20balance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20CATCH%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20for%20reforestation%20in%20the%20NSG%20campus%20are%20a%20step%20towards%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20blueprint%20for%20building%20a%20forest%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20forest%2C%20having%20trees%20of%20varying%20heights%20is%20good%20from%20two%20standpoints%20%E2%80%94%20they%20support%20different%20species%2C%20and%20they%20influence%20different%20levels%20of%20light%20and%20water%20availability.%20The%20CATCH%20Foundation%20model%20is%20cognisant%20of%20this.%20It%20accounts%20for%20plants%20of%20every%20height%2C%20from%20shrub%20layers%20(6%20feet)%20to%20the%20canopy%20layers%20(above%2040%20feet).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20steps%20of%20rewilding%20barren%20areas%20of%20land%20across%20India%20involve%20firstly%20narrowing%20down%20on%20areas%20which%20have%20been%20ridden%20by%20mining%20and%20de-forestation%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418898%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20steps%20of%20rewilding%20barren%20areas%20of%20land%20across%20India%20involve%20narrowing%20down%20areas%20which%20have%20been%20ridden%20by%20mining%20and%20deforestation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20inspection%20of%20the%20land%2C%20a%20land%20letter%20is%20acquired%20from%20the%20government.%20This%20documentation%20legally%20allows%20CATCH%20Foundation%20to%20lease%20the%20land%20and%20subject%20it%20to%20reforestation%20efforts.%20The%20next%20step%20is%20soil%20testing%20(and%20conducting%20a%20baseline%20survey%20of%20the%20site%20before%20plantation)%2C%20borewell%20digging%2C%20and%20then%20the%20creation%20of%20fencing%20systems%20to%20prevent%20any%20intervention%20from%20the%20local%20groups%20of%20domestic%20animals%20that%20might%20harm%20the%20plantation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CATCH%20team%20works%20on%20the%20project%20with%20post-plantation%20maintenance.%20They%20share%20that%20the%20team%20employs%20and%20trains%20local%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20ensures%20regular%20activities%20and%20ensures%20the%20forest%20is%20made%20self-sustainable%20in%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FByvdpRw4nMA%3Fsi%3DGdOmGtAyfjsgXeM6%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20followed%20by%20integrating%20solar%20systems%20(in%20some%20cases)%20to%20harness%20green%20power%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20